                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850406-52-defend586 t17850406-52-punish256"></join>
               Whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
